Tricky Problem because of the large test case.
1. Create a map: key: 1-25(Characters), value: List of words(Bit Mask) with this Character in it
2. Compute every word's bit mask
3. Compute every puzzle's bit mask and get the list from map by puzzle's first character, then traverse word mask and do a  `&` operation to check if the puzzle has all the characters the word contains. `count++`
