  (a,as,abel,abilty,act,acort,aces) -> Present in Trie

    Also while searching the count of words corresponding to puzzles[i], first we need to check presence of first char of puzzles[i], order of chars not matters, so we store the first char and sort the puzzles[i]

  Now lets search for count of words corresponds to actresz-> sorted(acerstz) , First_ch=a

  for(acerstz){
  a==First_ch (true) , move toward a , count=count+count of ew(at 'a')= 0+1=1
  c(First_ch 'a' already get(true)) , a->c(in trie) , count=count+count of ew(at 'c')=1+0=1
  e , a->c->e(in trie) , count=count+count of ew( at 'e')=1+0=1
  r , a->c->e->r , count=count + count of ew(at 'r')=1+0=1
  s , a->c->e->r->s, count=count+ count of ew (at 's')= 1+2(for "as" and "aces")=3
  t , a->c->e->r->s->t , count=count+ count of ew(at 't')=3+1(for "act")=4
  z , a->c->e->r->s->t->z , count=count+ count of ew (at 'z')= 4+0=4

  return count=4;

  }


